WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:25.280
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:37.090 --> 00:01:40.950
[Footprints of Change]

00:01:41.380 --> 00:01:43.840
[Episode 29]

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:52.460
Why didn't you invite your boyfriend in?

00:01:54.710 --> 00:01:56.479
He just came to bring me the keys.

00:01:56.479 --> 00:01:58.789
I left in a hurry and forgot to take them.

00:01:59.229 --> 00:02:01.830
Beichuan has night classes
at school tonight.

00:02:02.790 --> 00:02:03.870
He's quite funny.

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:06.060
He seems very attached to you.

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:10.120
I need to talk to him about this
when I get back.

00:02:10.120 --> 00:02:11.310
That was too rude.

00:02:11.310 --> 00:02:13.110
How could he come here directly?

00:02:15.020 --> 00:02:17.850
What book did you say
you wanted to show me?

00:02:24.630 --> 00:02:25.630
I'll go get it.

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:31.040
Is Shan Huajing home?

00:02:31.370 --> 00:02:32.150
Search warrant.

00:02:32.150 --> 00:02:32.840
Who is it?

00:02:36.060 --> 00:02:36.860
Ms. Shan.

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:39.600
Which one of you is Shan Huajing?

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:40.840
I am.

00:02:43.870 --> 00:02:44.710
Ms. Shan,

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:47.300
if there's nothing else, I'll get going.

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:48.360
Wait.

00:02:50.520 --> 00:02:52.120
What's your relationship
with Shan Huajing?

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:53.680
Why are you in her home?

00:03:00.710 --> 00:03:02.630
We went to the same school.

00:03:03.310 --> 00:03:04.350
She's my senior.

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:07.520
I just came to chat with her.

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:09.900
What's in your bag?

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:15.840
Open it.

00:03:45.470 --> 00:03:46.270
You can go now.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:56.740
Why are you crying?

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:02.150
I'm not feeling well.

00:04:03.800 --> 00:04:05.000
Then go home and rest.

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:06.970
We need to talk to Shan Huajing.

00:04:07.810 --> 00:04:08.250
Okay.

00:06:46.870 --> 00:06:48.000
Section Chief Shan,

00:06:48.070 --> 00:06:50.070
I just need a quick word with Xining.

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:01.740
Xiang Beichuan, what are you doing here?

00:07:02.430 --> 00:07:03.390
I'm asking you.

00:07:13.510 --> 00:07:14.680
Are you crazy?

00:09:15.510 --> 00:09:16.120
Jie.

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:17.710
Well,

00:09:17.740 --> 00:09:19.740
Ms. Shan is in trouble. Did you know?

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:23.680
Okay.

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:26.440
I'll let you know once I book the flight.

00:09:31.240 --> 00:09:32.200
Alright, thank you.

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:33.260
I'm hanging up now.

00:10:01.790 --> 00:10:04.190
This batch of goods
has a strict time limit.

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:05.920
Sea freight takes 40 days.

00:10:06.390 --> 00:10:08.190
If we wait another 30 days to send it out,

00:10:08.190 --> 00:10:09.820
it'll miss the sales window.

00:10:11.150 --> 00:10:11.960
Could you please

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:13.790
help us

00:10:13.870 --> 00:10:15.270
talk to your supervisor?

00:10:16.230 --> 00:10:18.150
Shan Huajing's case
hasn't been cleared yet.

00:10:18.150 --> 00:10:18.960
All our business dealings related to her

00:10:18.960 --> 00:10:20.510
are temporarily frozen.

00:10:20.680 --> 00:10:21.680
Sorry about that.

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:25.480
Okay, thank you.

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:39.670
Thank you.

00:10:40.190 --> 00:10:41.050
Have you eaten?

00:10:44.670 --> 00:10:45.510
Yes, I have.

00:10:49.310 --> 00:10:50.600
You should go to work now.

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:51.400
Don't be late.

00:10:59.030 --> 00:10:59.670
Are you...

00:10:59.690 --> 00:11:00.330
I'm fine.

00:11:01.150 --> 00:11:01.880
I'm alright.

00:11:46.600 --> 00:11:47.200
Beichuan.

00:11:48.390 --> 00:11:49.450
What is it, Mr. Guo?

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:52.240
Congratulations on your new book.

00:11:52.550 --> 00:11:54.280
Although it's your first work,

00:11:54.550 --> 00:11:55.440
I can see

00:11:55.870 --> 00:11:57.670
you have great literary talent.

00:11:58.670 --> 00:12:01.550
Your writing is smooth,
and your ideas are profound.

00:12:01.550 --> 00:12:03.270
I've read so many novels,

00:12:03.510 --> 00:12:05.000
but yours is the only one

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:07.130
worth reading repeatedly—

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:08.530
it keeps me captivated.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:10.690
Mr. Guo, you flatter me.

00:12:11.160 --> 00:12:12.790
Guys, come out!

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:14.480
Professor Xiang is here!

00:12:15.130 --> 00:12:15.770
Come on!

00:12:15.790 --> 00:12:16.460
Professor Xiang!

00:12:16.460 --> 00:12:18.030
Weren't you all asking for his autograph?

00:12:18.030 --> 00:12:19.120
Line up and get it one by one.

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:19.750
Hurry!

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:20.390
Okay.

00:12:22.870 --> 00:12:24.720
Professor Xiang, congratulations.

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:26.630
Your work is really excellent.

00:12:26.910 --> 00:12:28.440
Could you sign this for me?

00:12:36.440 --> 00:12:36.890
Thank you.

00:12:36.890 --> 00:12:38.770
Sir, this is for my brother.

00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:40.130
His name is Zhao Xiaohu.

00:12:48.840 --> 00:12:50.300
Everyone, how about this?

00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:52.510
Please return to the classroom now.

00:12:52.510 --> 00:12:53.710
I'll see you in class.

00:12:54.630 --> 00:12:55.630
Professor Xiang,

00:12:55.800 --> 00:12:56.800
the students and I

00:12:57.150 --> 00:12:58.750
have a wish for you:

00:12:59.030 --> 00:13:02.490
May you keep writing tirelessly,
dedicating yourself fully,

00:13:02.630 --> 00:13:06.160
pouring your sweat onto both the podium
and the literary world.

00:13:08.870 --> 00:13:09.940
Thank you.

00:13:10.440 --> 00:13:11.080
Thank you.

00:13:39.910 --> 00:13:40.510
Mr. Yan.

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:42.600
Xining, come in.

00:13:46.390 --> 00:13:48.390
Here's the money you lent me before.

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:50.390
No need. Keep it for yourself.

00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:14.570
I'll be away for a while.

00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:15.670
Take care of yourself.

00:14:15.670 --> 00:14:16.800
Where are you going?

00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:20.240
Guangzhou, Shenzhen, Hong Kong—

00:14:20.270 --> 00:14:22.200
I have friends in all these places.

00:14:23.040 --> 00:14:24.550
I'll leave you a phone number later.

00:14:24.550 --> 00:14:25.750
If anything urgent comes up,

00:14:25.750 --> 00:14:26.810
just give me a call.

00:14:28.490 --> 00:14:29.890
Okay. I'll be going then.

00:14:36.590 --> 00:14:40.200
[Beichuan's New Book Signing:
Rise and Fall of the Tide]

00:14:43.510 --> 00:14:44.150
Thank you.

00:14:49.840 --> 00:14:50.550
Thanks.

00:14:50.960 --> 00:14:52.090
Hello. This is mine.

00:14:54.550 --> 00:14:55.270
Thank you.

00:14:56.750 --> 00:14:58.350
Hello, Professor Beichuan.

00:15:00.270 --> 00:15:00.910
Thank you.

00:15:00.930 --> 00:15:02.210
Professor Xiang, I really admire you.

00:15:02.210 --> 00:15:02.810
Thank you.

00:15:09.030 --> 00:15:09.750
Jerk,

00:15:09.820 --> 00:15:11.270
isn't this your paper?

00:15:12.600 --> 00:15:14.460
This jerk's paper got published.

00:15:15.470 --> 00:15:16.930
Sir, I'll take ten copies.

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:19.120
Why so many?

00:15:19.440 --> 00:15:20.390
Can you even read them all?

00:15:20.390 --> 00:15:21.780
I'm giving them to others as gifts.

00:15:21.780 --> 00:15:22.300
Come on.

00:15:22.550 --> 00:15:24.480
We don't need to be so vain.

00:15:25.720 --> 00:15:26.670
You're not vain?

00:15:27.030 --> 00:15:28.150
You don't want to be famous?

00:15:28.150 --> 00:15:29.190
To be honest,

00:15:29.750 --> 00:15:31.050
fame doesn't matter much

00:15:31.050 --> 00:15:32.100
to me.

00:15:32.630 --> 00:15:33.670
My main task

00:15:33.670 --> 00:15:35.360
is to turn my observations into papers

00:15:35.360 --> 00:15:37.540
that readers can engage with,
and that's enough.

00:15:37.540 --> 00:15:38.450
I'm vain.

00:15:38.470 --> 00:15:40.220
I'm proud that your book got published.

00:15:40.220 --> 00:15:42.420
This is called "when fortune comes..."

00:15:42.420 --> 00:15:43.750
"We forget each other."

00:15:44.510 --> 00:15:45.910
Don't talk to me today.

00:15:46.970 --> 00:15:48.370
Why are you angry?

00:15:49.460 --> 00:15:51.010
[A strange twist of fate]

00:15:51.040 --> 00:15:53.100
[brought Beichuan and me together.]

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:56.090
[He walked with me for a long stretch.]

00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:58.310
[But as I kept going,]

00:15:58.920 --> 00:16:00.780
[I drifted further and further.]

00:16:01.250 --> 00:16:02.520
[When I looked back,]

00:16:03.270 --> 00:16:05.470
[Beichuan was still in the same place.]

00:16:06.710 --> 00:16:09.110
[It's not that
he couldn't keep up with me.]

00:16:09.440 --> 00:16:11.080
[I lost him.]

00:16:13.550 --> 00:16:15.680
[Actually, I was the one who got lost.]

00:16:15.840 --> 00:16:17.240
[Now, for me,]

00:16:17.240 --> 00:16:18.270
[parting]

00:16:18.570 --> 00:16:20.170
[is more dignified.]

00:16:31.480 --> 00:16:32.200
Jiuling,

00:16:33.150 --> 00:16:34.200
you were right.

00:16:35.240 --> 00:16:37.240
I'm really not cut out for business.

00:16:38.150 --> 00:16:40.350
I've already closed down this company,

00:16:40.660 --> 00:16:44.390
and the equipment in the factory
has all been mortgaged to the bank.

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:46.930
So what are you planning to do next?

00:16:47.440 --> 00:16:48.440
I'll just accept my fate

00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:49.900
and go back to my old trade—

00:16:50.120 --> 00:16:51.380
the textile industry.

00:16:52.080 --> 00:16:53.480
I'll open a small factory

00:16:53.840 --> 00:16:55.500
and focus only on production.

00:16:56.310 --> 00:16:58.090
Then in the future,
when we get stock from you,

00:16:58.090 --> 00:16:59.670
you'll have to give us a discount.

00:16:59.670 --> 00:17:00.630
Of course.

00:17:00.840 --> 00:17:01.830
You can't make a profit from us.

00:17:01.830 --> 00:17:03.270
I'll give you factory price.

00:17:03.270 --> 00:17:03.800
Alright.

00:17:04.069 --> 00:17:04.670
By the way,

00:17:05.339 --> 00:17:06.849
the lease on this place isn't up yet.

00:17:06.849 --> 00:17:08.310
You guys can keep using it.

00:17:10.730 --> 00:17:11.420
Thank you.

00:17:12.480 --> 00:17:13.630
I've been limping along with you—

00:17:13.630 --> 00:17:14.829
I'm almost crippled.

00:17:17.240 --> 00:17:19.589
You should rent
a single-story house next time.

00:17:19.589 --> 00:17:20.680
Your leg isn't good.

00:17:20.680 --> 00:17:22.109
This won't do.

00:17:22.170 --> 00:17:22.960
Right.

00:17:23.750 --> 00:17:25.160
Once you get that small factory running,

00:17:25.160 --> 00:17:26.420
you'll be really busy.

00:17:27.109 --> 00:17:29.590
[Mr. Lu left with ease.]

00:17:30.160 --> 00:17:31.380
[This is both a farewell]

00:17:31.380 --> 00:17:32.550
[and a beginning.]

00:18:28.130 --> 00:18:29.200
[Xiang Beichuan,]

00:18:29.890 --> 00:18:31.370
[I lost pretty badly.]

00:18:32.110 --> 00:18:34.510
[All I have left
is the visa Yan Jun gave me.]

00:18:34.670 --> 00:18:36.000
[I want to give it a try.]

00:18:36.420 --> 00:18:37.730
[I hope I can succeed.]

00:18:39.010 --> 00:18:39.940
[Let's]

00:18:40.830 --> 00:18:41.750
[break up.]

00:18:42.690 --> 00:18:44.820
[I hope everything goes well for you.]

00:20:09.560 --> 00:20:13.240
[One year later]

00:20:36.880 --> 00:20:37.810
Xiang Beichuan!

00:20:38.310 --> 00:20:39.640
I've missed you so much!

00:20:40.110 --> 00:20:41.030
Did you miss me?

00:20:44.360 --> 00:20:44.960
I didn't.

00:20:44.980 --> 00:20:45.780
You're lying.

00:20:47.350 --> 00:20:48.480
Why would I lie to you?

00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:49.740
Why didn't you miss me?

00:20:50.090 --> 00:20:51.290
Why should I miss you?

00:20:51.350 --> 00:20:53.480
I went to the old house looking for you.

00:20:53.720 --> 00:20:54.850
Why did you move out?

00:20:55.240 --> 00:20:55.640
Yes.

00:20:57.200 --> 00:20:57.860
I moved out.

00:20:59.380 --> 00:21:00.400
Why are you looking for me?

00:21:00.400 --> 00:21:01.400
To date you.

00:21:02.190 --> 00:21:03.230
I've made money.

00:21:03.260 --> 00:21:05.060
I've made lots and lots of money.

00:21:05.610 --> 00:21:07.210
Come on. Let's go to the mall.

00:21:07.240 --> 00:21:09.380
The outfit you're wearing
is the one I bought you before.

00:21:09.380 --> 00:21:10.450
I'll get you a new one,

00:21:10.450 --> 00:21:11.210
a designer brand,

00:21:11.210 --> 00:21:12.410
and pair it with a bag.

00:21:12.620 --> 00:21:13.870
Tonight, we'll go out to eat

00:21:13.870 --> 00:21:15.480
at the best restaurant in Shanghai.

00:21:15.480 --> 00:21:16.880
Order whatever you want.

00:21:17.920 --> 00:21:18.450
Let's go.

00:21:22.350 --> 00:21:23.610
What's wrong with you?

00:21:34.900 --> 00:21:37.790
[Fuxing Restaurant]

00:21:39.340 --> 00:21:40.060
Mr. Yan.

00:21:40.270 --> 00:21:41.440
Come, have a seat.

00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:51.030
How's the jet lag?

00:21:52.790 --> 00:21:53.510
Not so good.

00:21:57.520 --> 00:21:59.180
Have you seen Xiang Beichuan?

00:22:01.160 --> 00:22:01.820
Yes, I have.

00:22:02.640 --> 00:22:03.370
How did it go?

00:22:05.880 --> 00:22:06.610
Pretty well.

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:08.200
Pretty well, huh?

00:22:09.720 --> 00:22:11.480
I ordered

00:22:11.620 --> 00:22:12.640
sweet and sour spare ribs

00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:13.750
and smoked fish for you.

00:22:13.750 --> 00:22:15.350
They're all your favorites.

00:22:15.440 --> 00:22:16.900
The taste hasn't changed.

00:22:17.720 --> 00:22:19.580
They haven't changed their chef?

00:22:19.650 --> 00:22:20.780
It's still Chef Liu.

00:22:24.550 --> 00:22:25.240
Mr. Yan, I heard

00:22:25.240 --> 00:22:27.680
you're still working at the old house.

00:22:28.910 --> 00:22:30.960
You're such an accomplished entrepreneur—

00:22:30.960 --> 00:22:33.760
why didn't you move
to a top-tier office building?

00:22:35.610 --> 00:22:37.200
I quite like the old house

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:38.270
because

00:22:38.910 --> 00:22:40.970
it holds so many wonderful memories.

00:22:42.030 --> 00:22:42.830
How about you?

00:22:42.830 --> 00:22:44.750
Where are you working
now that you're back?

00:22:44.750 --> 00:22:46.310
I had Jiuling renew the lease

00:22:46.310 --> 00:22:47.570
on Mr. Lu's old office.

00:22:48.360 --> 00:22:50.190
One reason is convenience;

00:22:50.830 --> 00:22:51.690
another is that

00:22:51.750 --> 00:22:53.960
I started my business here before,

00:22:54.390 --> 00:22:57.540
and now that I'm back,
I want to start fresh here again.

00:22:59.960 --> 00:23:02.270
Looks like we're both sentimental people.

00:23:02.270 --> 00:23:03.600
We're still neighbors.

00:23:04.070 --> 00:23:06.480
We'll have to help each other out at work.

00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:09.080
Don't worry. If there's anything I can do,

00:23:09.230 --> 00:23:10.160
just let me know.

00:23:24.100 --> 00:23:25.030
During this past year,

00:23:25.030 --> 00:23:27.360
have you been in touch with Beichuan much?

00:23:27.480 --> 00:23:29.940
He and his senior
opened a cultural company.

00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:31.460
I wonder how it turned out.

00:23:32.550 --> 00:23:34.950
I haven't kept in touch
with Beichuan much.

00:23:39.160 --> 00:23:40.550
I invite you to dinner,

00:23:40.960 --> 00:23:42.160
and you don't ask how I'm doing

00:23:42.160 --> 00:23:44.580
but keep asking about Xiang Beichuan.
That's not appropriate.

00:23:44.580 --> 00:23:45.840
I was just about to ask.

00:23:46.030 --> 00:23:47.030
How have you been?

00:23:48.370 --> 00:23:49.010
Not good.

00:23:49.640 --> 00:23:51.350
I've been single all this time.

00:23:51.350 --> 00:23:52.590
That can't be true.

00:23:54.030 --> 00:23:55.720
You're so handsome

00:23:55.720 --> 00:23:56.550
and charming,

00:23:56.550 --> 00:23:58.230
surrounded by beautiful women.

00:23:58.230 --> 00:24:00.290
You're the least likely to be single.

00:24:00.350 --> 00:24:02.610
I've been single in spirit all this time.

00:24:02.790 --> 00:24:05.320
It's just that
I've had a lot of social events.

00:24:08.200 --> 00:24:09.480
Alright,
it's been a year since we last met.

00:24:09.480 --> 00:24:11.200
We've caught up enough.

00:24:11.350 --> 00:24:12.210
Are you hungry?

00:24:13.590 --> 00:24:14.200
Waitress.

00:24:14.710 --> 00:24:15.770
Hurry up with the dishes.

00:24:15.770 --> 00:24:16.570
Alright, sir.

00:24:19.220 --> 00:24:19.850
Li.

00:24:22.110 --> 00:24:22.750
Mr. Yan.

00:24:28.510 --> 00:24:29.370
Xining is back.

00:24:30.840 --> 00:24:31.510
Take good care of her.

00:24:31.510 --> 00:24:32.040
Alright.

00:24:32.470 --> 00:24:33.400
Split it between you two.

00:24:33.400 --> 00:24:34.310
Okay. Thank you, Mr. Yan.

00:24:34.310 --> 00:24:35.240
Enjoy your meal.

00:24:36.360 --> 00:24:38.020
You really deserve your name.

00:24:40.640 --> 00:24:42.500
This is the new

00:24:42.530 --> 00:24:44.460
clothing export company I set up
after coming back.

00:24:44.460 --> 00:24:45.350
Take a look

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:48.540
and see
if you're interested in collaborating.

00:24:51.350 --> 00:24:52.790
Whatever your first deal is

00:24:52.790 --> 00:24:53.850
after coming back,

00:24:54.030 --> 00:24:55.360
I'll fully support you.

00:24:59.960 --> 00:25:01.150
I'll toast you with tea.

00:25:01.150 --> 00:25:02.750
Just have some wine—why tea?

00:25:03.110 --> 00:25:04.840
I can't. I'll be driving later.

00:25:05.060 --> 00:25:05.690
Fine,

00:25:06.140 --> 00:25:06.930
tea it is.

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:16.720
Beichuan.

00:25:18.550 --> 00:25:19.310
I'm here.

00:25:21.790 --> 00:25:24.320
If you're thirsty,
pour yourself some water.

00:25:26.400 --> 00:25:27.870
Why are you living here?

00:25:33.270 --> 00:25:36.160
I'm seeking inspiration among mortals.

