00:28:12.710 --> 00:28:14.710
She'd feel so happy.

00:28:15.170 --> 00:28:16.900
She's not that materialistic.

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:30.540
Do you think

00:28:32.150 --> 00:28:33.880
the differences between women

00:28:34.570 --> 00:28:35.920
can be that big?

00:28:36.030 --> 00:28:36.880
Of course.

00:28:39.350 --> 00:28:40.680
What about between men?

00:28:45.240 --> 00:28:46.040
It's the same.

00:28:55.680 --> 00:28:56.920
I don't think so.

