00:29:47.030 --> 00:29:48.230
So it must be for love.

00:29:49.830 --> 00:29:51.360
You came back for Beichuan.

00:29:51.830 --> 00:29:53.290
I didn't come back for him.

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:55.440
Xining,

00:29:55.830 --> 00:29:57.270
I read a book the other day,

00:29:57.270 --> 00:29:59.170
and it said some really good things.

00:29:59.170 --> 00:30:00.570
It said that

00:30:00.720 --> 00:30:03.120
a woman shouldn't imagine a man
as perfect,

00:30:03.310 --> 00:30:05.570
because he can't be perfect in real life.

00:30:06.030 --> 00:30:08.490
That would just put too much pressure
on him.

00:30:08.680 --> 00:30:10.240
For a woman,

00:30:10.920 --> 00:30:12.920
if she loves too intensely,

00:30:13.750 --> 00:30:15.550
she becomes too sensitive.

00:30:16.550 --> 00:30:17.960
Even the tiniest crack

00:30:18.590 --> 00:30:20.200
gets magnified by her.

00:30:23.000 --> 00:30:24.550
And what about men?

00:30:25.000 --> 00:30:25.960
It's the same.

00:30:26.230 --> 00:30:27.030
Think about it—

00:30:27.030 --> 00:30:29.640
if a man treats you like a goddess—

00:30:30.550 --> 00:30:32.410
but you're not actually a goddess

00:30:32.430 --> 00:30:34.070
and have so many flaws—

00:30:34.350 --> 00:30:37.680
doesn't that make you exhausted
and under a lot of pressure?

00:30:39.030 --> 00:30:40.030
And his love

00:30:40.030 --> 00:30:42.480
will also be intense.

00:30:43.030 --> 00:30:45.580
Then he'll become very sensitive.

00:30:46.510 --> 00:30:47.310
Then

00:30:47.720 --> 00:30:49.200
even the tiniest crack

00:30:49.880 --> 00:30:51.740
will get magnified by him as well.

00:30:55.160 --> 00:30:56.510
So are you saying

00:30:57.120 --> 00:30:59.060
men and women

00:30:59.790 --> 00:31:01.520
shouldn't love too intensely?

00:31:01.550 --> 00:31:02.270
No.

00:31:03.110 --> 00:31:04.510
Then what are you saying?

00:31:06.350 --> 00:31:07.640
Love is about managing

00:31:08.090 --> 00:31:09.620
and exercising restraint.

00:31:33.440 --> 00:31:34.110
Mr. Guo,

00:31:34.510 --> 00:31:35.970
I believe this is my class.

00:31:36.070 --> 00:31:37.070
Professor Xiang.

00:31:37.140 --> 00:31:38.160
Come here.

00:31:45.510 --> 00:31:46.160
Beichuan,

00:31:46.550 --> 00:31:47.750
about the apartment,

00:31:48.000 --> 00:31:49.860
I've always been grateful to you.

00:31:51.310 --> 00:31:51.960
Today,

00:31:51.960 --> 00:31:54.200
