I said I wouldn't come,

00:31:56.200 --> 00:31:58.200
but everyone in our department

00:31:58.680 --> 00:31:59.790
insisted.

00:31:59.970 --> 00:32:01.830
They said only my teaching skills

00:32:01.880 --> 00:32:03.640
are on the same level as yours.

00:32:04.590 --> 00:32:05.510
Mr. Guo,

00:32:06.100 --> 00:32:07.700
you're substituting for me?

00:32:09.550 --> 00:32:10.400
I know about

00:32:11.010 --> 00:32:12.140
that thing of yours.

00:32:12.480 --> 00:32:14.000
Others might think

00:32:14.940 --> 00:32:16.450
it's kind of shady,

00:32:16.960 --> 00:32:18.110
but to me,

00:32:18.340 --> 00:32:19.660
you're very brave

00:32:20.110 --> 00:32:21.310
when it comes to love.

00:32:22.270 --> 00:32:25.130
I've always thought
you're a truly genuine person.

00:32:27.480 --> 00:32:28.270
What thing?

00:32:28.880 --> 00:32:31.340
How come I don't even know about this
myself?

00:32:35.070 --> 00:32:36.400
Love in Partition Room.

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:39.330
Love in Partition Room?

00:32:42.200 --> 00:32:44.930
Professor Xiang,
could you come out for a moment?

00:32:50.640 --> 00:32:51.480
It's been a pleasure working with you.

