But you mixed real people's looks, jobs,

00:38:46.280 --> 00:38:47.340
and personalities

00:38:47.510 --> 00:38:49.190
with fictional plots.

00:38:49.670 --> 00:38:51.670
It's impossible not to make people think
it's about a specific person.

00:38:51.670 --> 00:38:53.130
And you included all of us.

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:54.480
Yes.

00:38:54.880 --> 00:38:57.080
You even wrote that I'm like a horny dog.

00:38:57.280 --> 00:38:58.740
We barely know each other.

00:38:58.880 --> 00:39:00.190
I didn't write about you.

00:39:00.190 --> 00:39:02.150
You're the one reading yourself into it.

00:39:02.150 --> 00:39:03.680
It has nothing to do with me.

00:39:04.880 --> 00:39:05.760
Tong Tong,

00:39:06.110 --> 00:39:07.570
we've consulted a lawyer.

00:39:07.590 --> 00:39:08.900
If a lot of people believe

00:39:08.900 --> 00:39:10.670
your novel is about a specific person,

00:39:10.670 --> 00:39:12.190
and that person suffers
negative consequences

00:39:12.190 --> 00:39:13.590
because of your work,

00:39:14.480 --> 00:39:16.000
they could sue you

00:39:16.150 --> 00:39:17.080
for defamation.

00:39:18.510 --> 00:39:20.760
I don't know these things.

00:39:21.030 --> 00:39:23.800
I thought that as long as
I put at the beginning of the novel,

00:39:23.800 --> 00:39:25.210
"This story is purely fictional;

00:39:25.210 --> 00:39:28.110
please don't read yourself into it,"
it would be fine.

00:39:28.110 --> 00:39:28.710
Besides,

00:39:28.960 --> 00:39:30.670
Professor Xiang is such a good person.

00:39:30.670 --> 00:39:32.320
How could I possibly harm him?

00:39:32.320 --> 00:39:33.360
Professor Xiang

00:39:33.750 --> 00:39:35.910
has now resigned because of you.

00:39:36.760 --> 00:39:39.690
Back when you were selling shirts
in the school dorm,

00:39:39.920 --> 00:39:42.960
Professor Xiang
used his school apartment quota

00:39:42.960 --> 00:39:43.820
to protect you,

00:39:44.150 --> 00:39:45.800
so you didn't get punished by the school.

00:39:45.800 --> 00:39:46.880
What did you say?

00:39:47.440 --> 00:39:49.880
You can check with the school
if it's true or not.

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:51.080
What you need to do now

00:39:51.360 --> 00:39:53.150
is write a formal statement

00:39:53.630 --> 00:39:57.110
clarifying that the story's main character
isn't Xiang Beichuan.

00:39:57.110 --> 00:39:59.040
That way, even though he resigned,

00:39:59.400 --> 00:40:00.670
he won't be too embarrassed

00:40:00.670 --> 00:40:02.150
when he meets his old colleagues

00:40:02.150 --> 00:40:03.610
or students in the future.

00:40:04.030 --> 00:40:05.000
I know.

00:40:05.320 --> 00:40:06.280
I'll do it.

00:40:06.480 --> 00:40:07.960
I don't need you to tell me that.

00:40:07.960 --> 00:40:10.960
Don't act like you're the only one
who cares about him.

00:40:39.150 --> 00:40:40.350
What are you here for?

00:40:41.700 --> 00:40:43.880
Professor Xiang...

00:40:45.960 --> 00:40:46.710
I'm sorry.

00:40:47.430 --> 00:40:49.030
I don't accept your apology.

00:40:49.800 --> 00:40:51.050
You can go back to class now.

00:40:51.050 --> 00:40:53.580
I've already been disciplined
by the school.

00:40:57.020 --> 00:40:58.460
Professor Xiang,

00:40:59.960 --> 00:41:00.670
here's...

00:41:01.110 --> 00:41:03.670
here's all my royalties.

00:41:04.210 --> 00:41:05.580
I'm giving it all to you.

00:41:06.230 --> 00:41:07.800
It's all because of me

00:41:08.060 --> 00:41:09.320
that you lost your job.

00:41:09.320 --> 00:41:10.580
Take it, just to get by.

00:41:10.610 --> 00:41:11.670
Stop following me.

00:41:19.540 --> 00:41:21.190
Do you really have to keep ruining me

00:41:21.190 --> 00:41:23.790
over and over
until I'm completely disgraced?

00:41:25.190 --> 00:41:26.000
I don't.

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:29.280
Xiang Bei...

00:41:29.510 --> 00:41:30.570
Stop following me.

00:41:31.630 --> 00:41:32.230
Tong Tong,

00:41:32.660 --> 00:41:34.390
are you really going to destroy

00:41:34.550 --> 00:41:36.060
the last bit of student-teacher bond

00:41:36.060 --> 00:41:36.980
we have left?

00:41:37.070 --> 00:41:37.630
I...

00:41:37.630 --> 00:41:38.590
As a girl,

00:41:39.360 --> 00:41:41.490
I hope you can show some self-respect.

00:41:44.020 --> 00:41:44.760
Alright.

00:41:44.890 --> 00:41:47.560
Can we still be friends?

00:41:47.590 --> 00:41:48.920
Are you out of your mind?

00:41:48.950 --> 00:41:49.620
No!